        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Both platforms serve the Indian hiring market with proctored assessments. Mercer Mettl is a broad enterprise exam platform with 26+ question formats and deep remote-invigilation capabilities. AssessIQ focuses on structured, rubric-based hiring assessments — anchor scoring, band-level rationale, and an admin-centric workflow — with pricing calibrated for Indian team sizes rather than global enterprise contracts."
      }
    },
