      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which platform has better proctoring — AssessIQ or Mettl?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Mercer Mettl's proctoring is one of its strongest features — AI-flagged anomalies, facial recognition, and 3-point candidate authentication, with claimed 98%+ accuracy. AssessIQ's proctoring covers tab-switch detection, webcam monitoring, full-screen enforcement, and a timestamped event log. For very high-stakes certification exams requiring forensic-grade invigilation, Mettl's investment in this area is well documented. For standard hiring-stage proctoring, AssessIQ's controls are purpose-built and sufficient."
